![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/28ac35ab-db89-422d-b94a-829953d523dd/20240413_030841.jpg?format=original)

New Japan Pro Wrestling has announced the IWGP World Heavyweight Champion Jon Moxley will return to the promotion for the Wrestling Dontaku double shot in Fukuoka International Center on May 3rd and May 4th.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5a0aea06-7f7d-4bcb-a7b2-94d3ebd61682/20240415_030308.jpg?format=original)

## Wrestling Dontaku on May 3rd

**_IWGP GLOBAL CHAMPIONSHIP_**:

Nic Nemeth vs Hiroshi Tanahashi

Yota Tsuji vs David Finlay

**_NJPW WORLD TV CHAMPIONSHIP:_**

ZSJ vs Jeff Cobb

Jon Moxley, Shota Umino and El Desperado vs HOUSE OF TORTURE

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7632d33d-0dfb-48ab-a83c-3e1807e60927/20240415_030338.jpg?format=original)

## WRESTLING DONTAKU ON MAY 4TH

**_IWGP WORLD HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP:_**

Jon Moxley vs Ren Narita

**_NEVER OPENWEIGHT CHAMPIONSHIP:_**

Gabe Kidd vs Shingo Takagi

**_IWGP TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS:_**

Bishamon vs KENTA and Chase Owens

Nic Nemeth and Hiroshi Tanahashi vs SANADA and Taichi